These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, sports, horror
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, april, december
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
3. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the person watching epic movies##7
4. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | horror       | mystery | epic        |
| Birthday      | april  | august | december        | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, purple, turquise, black
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, blues, classical, electronic
1. the fan electronic is somewhere between the fan classical and the person who likes turquise##7
2. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
3. the person who likes black is somewhere to the right of the fan electronic##5
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes black##1
5. the fan electronic is between the fan classical and the fan blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Color     | turquise | purple       | black         | amber     |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | electronic | classical | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, videographer, teacher, coach
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, drawing, writing
1. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the coach##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the videographer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Job   | videographer | coach | teacher | social-worker  |
| Hobby   | drawing | hiking  | writing   | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
City: rome, marseilles, venice, liverpool
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, snooker, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person traveling to liverpool##7
3. the person traveling to venice is the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| City   | marseilles | rome | liverpool       | venice |
| Game   | poker      | monopoly   | snooker | billiard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, august, january, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts, satire, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in october##7
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday         | january | october   | june | august |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero      | martial-arts | disaster      | satire |

