.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, security-guard, pilot, project-manager
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, april, may
1. the pilot is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the project-manager##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the police-officer##1
4. the police-officer is on the left of the pilot##1
5. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
6. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in october##7
7. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the pilot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job      | security-guard | police-officer      | pilot | project-manager     |
| Birthday   | september    | may | october   | april |

