.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, electronic, soul
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, fisherman, security-guard, electrician
1. the architect is on the far left##1
2. the fan indie is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the fan soul is on the far left or far right##3
4. the electrician is somewhere between the fan dubstep and the fan electronic##7
5. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the fan electronic##5
6. the electrician is on the left or right of the security-guard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre          | soul    | dubstep   | indie | electronic  |
| Job   | architect | security-guard | electrician    | fisherman |

