.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, metal, punk, salsa
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, brown, black, pink
1. the fan metal is not the person who likes pink##6
2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
3. the fan salsa is the person who likes black##1
4. the fan punk is somewhere between the fan salsa and the fan techno##7
5. the fan metal is on the left of the fan techno##1
6. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | punk | metal | techno |
| Color           | black   | pink    | blood-red       | brown  |

