.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, cycling, volleyball, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, airplane, van, bike
1. the person who's sport is swimming is not the person driving the car##6
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Sport           | soccer | swimming | volleyball | cycling |
| Transport   | bike         | van      | car | airplane            |

