.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, tea, mirinda
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, futuristic, craftsman
1. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the craftsman house##7
2. the person drinking water is not the futuristic house##6
3. the cape-cod house is not the person drinking tea##6
4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
5. the person drinking fanta is the ranch-style house##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | mirinda | water | tea |
| House           | ranch-style    | cape-cod   | craftsman  | futuristic      |

