.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, radish, carrot, grapefruit
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, airplane, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
5. the person eating spinach is between the person eating radish and the person driving the snowmobile##2
6. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person eating radish##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Food   | grapefruit | spinach | radish | carrot   |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | airplane      | roller      | quad-bike |

