2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
3. the cottage house is not the person who likes pink##6
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the modern house##1
5. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
6. the person who likes purple is somewhere between the person who likes pink and the person who likes lavender##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Color   | lavender | purple | fuchsia | pink |
| House   | cottage  | modern    | futuristic    | townhouse  |

