.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
House: cape-cod, modern, art-deco, gothic-revival
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, almond-milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is the art-deco house##1
4. the art-deco house is not the person drinking mirinda##6
5. the art-deco house is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the art-deco house##7
7. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| House       | gothic-revival | cape-cod | modern | art-deco |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk      | mirinda        | almond-milk  |

