2. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the person who likes amber and the person traveling to liverpool##7
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
4. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
6. the person who likes white is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person who likes yellow is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Color      | white   | chestnut | yellow | amber   |
| City   | miami | liverpool   | boston | london |

