2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who likes coral##7
5. the person who likes blue is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person who's hobby is fishing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Hobby           | fishing | filmmaking | reading | collecting  |
| Color   | coral     | blue   | white    | purple |

