The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, comedy, spy
1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the owner of the lizard##7
2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching spy movies##2
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
6. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Pet    | lizard   | ferret  | hedgehog  | dog |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | comedy | adventure | spy    |

