.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
House: victorian, townhouse, art-deco, ranch-style
City: venice, hamburg, edinburgh, marseilles
1. the art-deco house is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the townhouse house##7
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
5. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| House         | townhouse    | art-deco | ranch-style     | victorian |
| City   | edinburgh | marseilles  | hamburg | venice |

 